{"tid":414861,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2017老散獨白","createTime":"2017-09-26T13:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T16:44:43.000Z","uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9de2b99ebad7ddf59e48e26d8f8de277b10ba870","tid":414861,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"開場白：在座有任何人士係金融海嘯裏面奶左野既，我回水比你，有邊個？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩今年係牛市，連升左8個月，未見災難，相信各位巴打都賺唔少。小弟玩到今日仲keep到三成以上既利潤，還算滿意，當然冇各位巴打咁進取🙇🏻贏多多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年贏錢係肯坐，輸錢係玩太盡。一買即贏固然開心，一坐到尾的確袋唔少，但係唔會次次都買中就升，好多時要耐心等候，未跌到止蝕，其實唔洗理。多數輸錢都係衰衝動貪心，唔跟rule，到位唔分段止賺仲要加注，到左要止蝕又心存僥倖，第二日會上返黎，而好多時聽日就會急插，今年回調四次，我就奶足四次野，10月奶四次野，人生有幾多個十月？好難頂！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身邊實有唔少朋友贏好多，玩期指、牛熊、認股證，但其實呢d好高風險，只要回調深小小就隨時萬劫不復，贏十次但輸一次就可以清你袋。我都有玩過，初次買期指死仔金就射飛彈，兩日插左成千點，穿曬線，就止蝕，結果大家都知道，但5位數既損失歷歷在目，刻在心上，一時之間放下，為追上損失，更容易出錯。投資書籍上講到心態一環，看似簡單，其實係最難，難在如何對抗人性，低買高賣好容易，但你就係做唔到，特別係加埋槓桿，更難控制，一子錯就做左人地既提款機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有機會待續...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝幕黑：輸淨小小，都當係贏。"},{"pid":"4accc2d720f072baf9f3f52d84433beaa830d83a","tid":414861,"uid":30841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:17:43.000Z","msg":"我而家都坐緊艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遇岩呢兩日調整都唔知要坐幾耐"},{"pid":"93deb93bc44b1adf82ad146cc38ab38475153d24","tid":414861,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"我想知你定1040贏得多"},{"pid":"31e444ee85fad36af43dd9dd40dccb169371a073","tid":414861,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我而家都坐緊艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遇岩呢兩日調整都唔知要坐幾耐</blockquote><br />\n好股唔怕坐，廢股早斬早著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69126daa1df076dd901cef42c377c46faa781fad","tid":414861,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"1357<br />\n1415<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7753f63152e51f700a571ae094ad0ebd09f0cc7","tid":414861,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知你定1040贏得多</blockquote><br />\n佢消失左，晴巴贏得多👍"},{"pid":"c0dd8c61f2da66e14788d822cb1f17b9468d74c1","tid":414861,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"太貪唔識分段止賺+1<br />\n股票就係咁，賺左都唔開心，只係因為賺少左。<br />\n呢幾日盈利少左接近6位數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad9e0ef5048e8bba5444689d370773a719a204e","tid":414861,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"三成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千金巴強"},{"pid":"b85e5082efe32084ee1a98612dd28e1a9ea26b4c","tid":414861,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千金巴強</blockquote><br />\n還要繼續向放任巴學習🙇🏻"},{"pid":"60cf250323d05d20d6cf404aa21da13092eb9c7b","tid":414861,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千金巴強</blockquote><br />\n還要繼續向放任巴學習🙇🏻</blockquote><br />\n你調轉講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cc4b324784e3a2af8d8b221487e3f1b7ab1093","tid":414861,"uid":144774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:53:02.000Z","msg":"新手買牛熊輸3成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37771c25c8e5ba775ae0d0c4d1898525912bde69","tid":414861,"uid":144774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手買牛熊輸3成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打輸5位數點追番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fr